        <abstract> 
<p>Asks questions related to movement in plants. The cotyledons of <hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi> offer a promising field for study.</p> 
            <p>Wonders why Julius von Sachs thinks bloom is a protection against insects.</p> 
<p>Encloses notes on the cotyledons of <hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi> species.</p> 
        </abstract>
